Sec. 7 October 1, 2026 8-13ii(a)
Sec. 8 October 1, 2026 8-37bb(a)
Sec. 9 October 1, 2026 8-37r(f)
Statement of Purpose:
To implement the recommendations of the Majority Leader's
Roundtable on Affordable Housing and make other changes to the
affordable housing statutes.
